HEADWORD: Locellate
<hw>Lo*cel"late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>locellus</ets> a compartment, dim. of <ets>locus</ets> a
place.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Divided into secondary compartments
or cells, as where one cavity is separated into several smaller
ones.</def>⟦br⟧
